From 0000000000000000000000000000000000000000 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Krzysztof Kozlowski <krzysztof.kozlowski@linaro.org>
Date: Tue, 7 Oct 2025 17:17:45 +0900
Subject: arm64: qcom_laptops.config: Enable SQUASHFS_XATTR for distros

Some distros, e.g. Ubuntu LiveCD, use extended attributes in squashfs
images.  It also might be necessary for distros using SELinux.  Enable
it, requested by Steev.

Signed-off-by: Krzysztof Kozlowski <krzysztof.kozlowski@linaro.org>
Signed-off-by: Neil Armstrong <neil.armstrong@linaro.org>
Signed-off-by: Abel Vesa <abel.vesa@oss.qualcomm.com>
---
 arch/arm64/configs/qcom_laptops.config | 1 +
 1 file changed, 1 insertion(+)

diff --git a/arch/arm64/configs/qcom_laptops.config b/arch/arm64/configs/qcom_laptops.config
index 807d128411a3..f8b969870eef 100644
--- a/arch/arm64/configs/qcom_laptops.config
+++ b/arch/arm64/configs/qcom_laptops.config
@@ -61,6 +61,7 @@ CONFIG_DM_CRYPT=m
 CONFIG_DMABUF_HEAPS_CMA=y
 
 # For Ubuntu/snap
+CONFIG_SQUASHFS_XATTR=y
 CONFIG_SQUASHFS_LZ4=y
 CONFIG_SQUASHFS_LZO=y
 CONFIG_SQUASHFS_XZ=y
-- 
2.53.0

